{"tid":1724581,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"雖然去留係交比前線決定 但我好希望前線可以守住中大","createTime":"2019-11-15T13:27:24.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-15T13:57:00.000Z","uid":17701,"like":13,"dislike":7,"uniUserReply":14,"replies":[{"pid":"a6ae9ea2172b6c334e0f17d19206e9970ecbe6fb","tid":1724581,"uid":17701,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-15T13:27:24.000Z","msg":"話棄就棄 咁當初守黎做咩<br />\n守住中大, 仲可以繼續封吐露港, 理大封隧 完美堵路<br />\n中大既象徵性好重要<br />\n如果棄城 就完被充公哂咁多日黎大家捐比中大+物資 大家研發同量產既守城防具<br />\n仲要被POPO 瘋狂搜HALL 到時要插贓嫁禍 屈你藏有攻擊性武器又得 屈你藏毒都我<br />\n無錯,你今日棄城可能無事 但上千上萬既手足可能就要坐冤獄<br />\n大家 就算中大生放棄我地 我地都唔可以放棄中大生<br />\n入去守城!!!!!!<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f34df410ff98d051941d0700c3b3c48b73480e79","tid":1724581,"uid":17701,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-15T13:28:07.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"be33081923230d61d4353229917a85dc67c32f09","tid":1724581,"uid":49300,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-15T13:28:12.000Z","msg":"堆"},{"pid":"65741463e09929e1b66e4d613956be5d94126dcd","tid":1724581,"uid":17701,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-15T13:28:46.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dru